ChangeList.Description: Changed the type of the **itemInsights** navigation property of [organizationSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/organizationsettings?view=graph-rest-beta) from **itemInsightsSettings**  to [insightsSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/insightssettings?view=graph-rest-beta).

Added a **peopleInsights** navigation property of the [insightsSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/insightssettings?view=graph-rest-beta) type to [organizationSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/organizationsettings?view=graph-rest-beta).

Added a [list](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/organizationsettings-list-peopleinsights?view=graph-rest-beta) operation to [insightsSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/insightssettings?view=graph-rest-beta) to list settings for people insights.

Add functionality to the [update](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/insightsSettings-update?view=graph-rest-beta) operation to update [insightsSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/insightssettings?view=graph-rest-beta) for people insights.
Added the **itemInsights** navigation property to the [userSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/userSettings?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **GET** operation to the [userInsightsSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/userInsightsSettings?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **PATCH** operation to the [userInsightsSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/userInsightsSettings?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the [userInsightsSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/userInsightsSettings?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and supported methods.
Added the **itemInsights** relationship to the [userSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/userSettings?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Changed the type of the **insights** navigation property of the [user](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/user?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource from [officeGraphInsights](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/officegraphinsights?view=graph-rest-1.0) to [itemInsights](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/iteminsights?view=graph-rest-1.0).
